00:31:36.170 --> 00:31:38.890
So she always made
two of everything.

00:31:38.890 --> 00:31:41.060
So she made one the
regular way that she wanted

00:31:41.060 --> 00:31:42.500
and one a different way.

00:31:42.500 --> 00:31:47.010
And I always used to
think, wow, that's wrong.

00:31:47.010 --> 00:31:51.290
Now he eats it because he has no
choice, because his wife is not

00:31:51.290 --> 00:31:53.430
going to make him
two of everything.

00:31:53.430 --> 00:31:56.210
So he either eats it or not.

00:31:56.210 --> 00:31:59.050
