00:32:04.840 --> 00:32:08.300
or whatever weren't good,
or duck wasn't good,

00:32:08.300 --> 00:32:11.260
or pheasant wasn't good.

00:32:11.260 --> 00:32:14.400
My wife grew up right on
the coast in Mississippi,

00:32:14.400 --> 00:32:15.520
in Gulf Port.

00:32:15.520 --> 00:32:18.050
And when we met,
I always thought

00:32:18.050 --> 00:32:20.810
