00:32:20.810 --> 00:32:23.080
And you could see the
ocean from her house,

00:32:23.080 --> 00:32:26.210
but she didn't eat fish.

00:32:26.210 --> 00:32:29.590
She would eat speckled trout
or she would eat red fish,

00:32:29.590 --> 00:32:33.190
but she wouldn't eat the
other fish from the gulf.

00:32:33.190 --> 00:32:34.820
